#%% md
# 04. Advanced Parsing with Knowledge

**Purpose:** This is the capstone challenge, fulfilling the new **Task 4 (Regional Complexity)**. It introduces Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) and provides the pipeline for the final submission.

**Student Experience:**
*   You will learn why global address parsing is difficult.
*   You will build a two-stage pipeline that first detects the country, then retrieves country-specific rules from a knowledge base to help the main model.
*   You will run this advanced approach on the **unlabeled final test set**.
*   You will generate your submission file and see your leaderboard score.

**Key Takeaway:** You will learn that some problems require smarter system design, not just better prompts or bigger models. You are being introduced to a core industry technique: **RAG**.

